title: OBJKT4OBJKT
description: OBJKT4OBJKT was an event ran in collaboration by DiverseNftArt and Hicetnunc on the weekend of March 26th until 28th 2021, in which artists were encouraged to mint their OBJKTs for free in order to swap with other artists and build a more diverse collection.

title: TheFEN
description: “The Fen” is a series of coordinated CryptoArt drops to encourage artists and collectors to transition their NFTs to a low-energy consumption blockchain.
